data.actual_result: There is an space in the top
data.expected_result: There shouldn't be an extra space in the top
data.short_description: Extra space in the beginning of debug log message
data.steps_to_repro: - Go to settings > the 3 dots > debug  - Share the debug log to a channel  - The debug log won't be sent as it would be more then 2000 characters  - You might also get a error called unable to preprocess file - click back (2 times) and you will be at that channel where you tried to share debug log - Long press the debug log
